BT /F2 10 Tf 50 598 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 50 584 Td (Purpose) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 564 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 550 Td (PsyberShield is a Python-based security visibility and response tool for small servers) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 536 Td (and web applications.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 522 Td (It supports HTTP/HTTPS scanning, passive crawling, detection of common website/server) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 508 Td (misconfigurations, WAF/firewall impact notes, incident log analysis for) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 494 Td (Apache/auth/systemd-style logs, continuous watch monitoring for logs/files/process) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 480 Td (activity, file integrity monitoring, baseline drift detection, secret exposure checks,) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 466 Td (report bundling, report notifications, and safe defensive fixes where possible.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 452 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 438 Td (The preferred CLI command is `pshield`. `psybershield` and `turan` remain) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 424 Td (compatibility aliases during the transition.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 410 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 396 Td (For a command-by-command usage guide, see) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 382 Td ([docs/turan-user-guide.md]\(docs/turan-user-guide.md\) and the matching PDF at) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 368 Td ([psybershield-user-guide.pdf]\(psybershield-user-guide.pdf\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 354 Td (For a short version history, see [docs/changelog.md]\(docs/changelog.md\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 340 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 326 Td (The core flow is:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 312 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 298 Td (1. Observe) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 284 Td (2. Classify) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 270 Td (3. Recommend) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 256 Td (4. Apply only safe reversible fixes) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 242 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 228 Td (Anything that changes the system must pass through one gate:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 214 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 200 Td (if finding.fix_level > allowed_fix_level:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 186 Td (    return "approval_required") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 172 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 158 Td (That gate lives in one place only: the remediation executor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 144 Td () Tj ET
endstream
