stream
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 744 Td (The remediation executor is the only module that can apply a fix.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 730 Td (It must enforce policy before any write, restart, or system change.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 716 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 702 Td (from __future__ import annotations) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 688 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 674 Td (from app.models import Finding, FixPlan, Policy) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 660 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 646 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 632 Td (def execute_fix\(finding: Finding, plan: FixPlan, policy: Policy\) -> str:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 618 Td (    # Single gate.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 604 Td (    if finding.fix_level > policy.allowed_fix_level:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 590 Td (        return "approval_required") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 576 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 562 Td (    if plan.fix_level > policy.allowed_fix_level:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 548 Td (        return "approval_required") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 534 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 520 Td (    if plan.fix_level >= 2 and policy.require_approval_for_level_2:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 506 Td (        return "approval_required") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 492 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 478 Td (    if plan.fix_level >= 3 and policy.block_level_3:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 464 Td (        return "blocked") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 450 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 436 Td (    if policy.require_backup_for_level_1 and plan.fix_level >= 1 and not plan.backup_path:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 422 Td (        return "blocked") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 408 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 394 Td (    if not plan.rollback_command:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 380 Td (        return "blocked") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 366 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 352 Td (    if plan.expected_impact.strip\(\) == "":) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 338 Td (        return "blocked") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 324 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 310 Td (    # Safe, reversible changes only.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 296 Td (    return "applied") Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 282 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 50 268 Td (Approval Flow) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 248 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 234 Td (Level 2 actions must be explicit:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 220 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 206 Td (1. A finding produces a FixPlan.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 192 Td (2. Policy marks the plan as requiring approval.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 178 Td (3. The approver reviews backup_path, rollback_command, and expected_impact.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 164 Td (4. The executor applies the change only after approval is recorded.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
